	<ul><li><a href="https://www.hiusa.org/membership/member-benefits" >Member Benefits</a></li><li><a href="https://www.hiusa.org/membership/ways-to-join" >Ways to Join</a></li><li><a href="https://www.hiayh.net/hiusassa/ssaapexmnucall?p_app_id=hiusassa&p_page_id=3005&p_clearcache=3005" target="_blank">Renew Your Membership</a></li><li><a href="https://www.hiusa.org/membership/lost-stolen-card" >Lost/Stolen Card</a></li><li><a href="https://www.hiayh.net/hiusassa/hiusamemssagroup.wizstep1" target="_blank">Group Membership</a></li><li><a href="https://www.hiayh.net/hiusassa/hiusamemotsreg.wizstep1" target="_blank">Register Membership</a></li><li><a href="https://www.hiayh.net/hiusassa/ssaauthmain.login_page" target="_blank">Member Log In</a></li>		</ul>
