              <div class="tagline">
                <div class="container"><span>WE BELIEVE IN THE POWER OF TRAVEL TO CREATE A MORE TOLERANT WORLD</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="container">
            <article>
              <h1>Welcome to Hostelling International USA</h1>
              <div class="half">
                <p>HI USA has more than 50 hostels in extraordinary locations nationwide, bringing together people from across the country and around the world.</p>
                <p>With free events and programs we can connect you to the well-known and the lesser-known corners of the USA, while meeting like-minded travelers from across the country and around the world.</p>
                <p>At HI USA, we believe that to get to know a place, you have to see it like a local sees it, hang out where the locals hang out, feel it like a local feels it.</p>
                <p>Let your HI USA hostel experience be unforgettable for the places you see and the people you meet.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="half omega">
                <figure class="plain">
                <video id="movie" src="https://player.vimeo.com/external/129468302.hd.mp4?s=7d721df404637ed8b42e6da282ca75db656cb439&profile_id=113" controls width="450" poster="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/520963309_640.jpg"></video>
                  <figcaption>
                    <p>Because when we spend a little time together, some pretty great things can happen.</p>
                  </figcaption>
                </figure>
              </div>
               <div class="news-block">
                <h2>HI USA News</h2>
                <div class="half">
                  <a href="https://www.hiusa.org/hostels/california/montara/point-montara-lighthouse-hostel/hostel-news/water-the-gardens-by-washing-laundry" class="floating-image-description">
                    <img src="https://www.hiusa.org/images/uploads/montara-flowers-thumbnail.jpg" alt="Pt Montara Flowers">
                    <div class="position">
                      <h3>VOTE NOW: HI Sustainability Fund Grant</h3>
                      <p>The Sustainability Fund grant would help us build a greywater irrigation system to water HI Point Montaras native plant gardens using recycled water from the hostels washing machines. Every load of laundry done at the hostel will help its on-site gardens to thrive. Vote now <span class="gt-sign">&gt;</span></p>
                    </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
